A 4chan emailer for new posts which include your selected keywords.

Requires:
-python3

How to use:
-"cd 4chan-newpost-emailbot"
-change "bot_mail.txt" with your email, password and email service provider's host
--important! you should enable unsecure access to provided email.You might want to create a dummy email address for this.
-write your keywords to "keywords.txt". Sepereate each keyword with whitespaces.
-write your reciver email list to "emails.txt". Seperate each email with whitespaces.
-run "python3 main.py"

Important! This bot currently collects posts from only /biz/. To collect from another topic, edit api url from main.py
